# "Noon Train" - 5:51  
# "Drowsy" - 3:37  
# "[[Organ Grinder's Swing]]" (Will Hudson, [[Irving Mills]], [[Mitchell Parish]]) - 2:55  
# "Mack 'N' Duff" - 5:10  
# "[[You're Driving Me Crazy]]" ([[Walter Donaldson]]) - 4:47
# "Light Blues" (Bill Jennings, Jack McDuff) - 6:01

